        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> the statusline should not be enabled in floating windows.\n\nGlobal statusline is not \"inherited\", so statusline is not shown in floatwins by default.\n\nIf a window-local option is set then the plugin has chosen to enable that option. Plugins can check `vim.api.nvim_win_get_config(win)` to decide if a window is a floating window, and then decide whether to set the window-local statusline.\n\n",
